                        android:pathData="M 24 47 C 30.7 47 36.8 44.1 41 39.5 C 41 37.9 39.8 36 38.3 35.3 L 29 31 C 29 31 27 33 24 33 C 21 33 19 31 19 31 L 9.7 35.3 C 8.2 35.9 7 37.8 7 39.5 C 11.2 44.1 17.3 47 24 47 Z"
