                        android:pathData="M 28 14 C 30.2 14 32 15.8 32 18 L 32 13 C 32 10.8 30.2 9 28 9 L 27.5 9 L 26.5 6.9 C 26.2 6.4 25.6 6.2 25.1 6.4 L 18.8 8.9 C 17.2 9.5 16 11.3 16 13 L 16 18 C 16 15.8 17.8 14 20 14 L 28 14 Z"
